swp_compiler_ss13.common.ast.nodes.unary

Interface ArrayIdentifierNode

  • All Superinterfaces:
    ASTNode, ExpressionNode, IdentifierNode, StatementNode
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    ArrayIdentifierNodeImpl

    public interface ArrayIdentifierNode
extends IdentifierNode
    The node to reference an array identifier. The index defines the index to access. The identifier itself is another IdentifierNode. This IdentifierNode can be a BasicIdentifierNode to access the first array level. It can be another ArrayIdentifierNode to access a multidimensional array or a StructIdentifierNode to access an array inside a struct.
    Author:
    "Frank Zechert"
